<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{> template/title}}</title>
</head>
<body>
{{> template/header}}
<section class="ht-section-main">
    <div class="dark-layer">
        <div class="ht-main-text">
            그곳에서 꼭 해야 할 한가지 Activity
        </div>
        <div class="ht-sub-text">
            여행지별 놓쳐서는 안될 액티비티를 확인해보세요.
        </div>
        <div class="ht-search-box">
            <input type="text" class="ht-search-main" placeholder="가고싶은 여행지, 투어, 액티비티를 검색해보세요.">
            <i class="ht-search-icon fa fa-search"></i>
        </div>
        <ul class="ht-download-app">
           <li>
               <img src="./img/play-logo.png" class="play-logo">
           </li>
           <li>
               <i class="fa fa-apple"></i>
               <span>Apple Store</span>
           </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="ht-section-char">
    <ul class="ht-characters">
        <li>
            <div class="ht-char-no">1</div>
            <img class="ht-character" src="./img/ic-step1.png">
            <div class="ht-character">
                여행지를 선택,<br>
                모든 액티비티를 한번에 확인
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="ht-char-no">2</div>
            <img class="ht-character" src="./img/ic-step2.png">
            <div class="ht-character">
                각 여행지, 액티비티의 정보,<br>
                사진, 후기를 한눈에 보기
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="ht-char-no">3</div>
            <img class="ht-character" src="./img/ic-step3.png">
            <div class="ht-character">
                빠르고 간편하게<br>
                예약 및 결재 완료
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
</section>
<section>
    <div class="ht-section-tt">
        지금 뜨는 <span>핫</span> Tours & Activities
    </div>
    <div class="ht-section-cont">
        <ul class="ht-hot-area">
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/hot-area1.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                진정한 우아함을<br>보고싶다면<br><strong>표범</strong>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/hot-area2.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    강인한 멋있음을<br>보고싶다면<br><strong>호랑이</strong>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/hot-area3.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    도도한 매력의 소유자<br>의외의 귀여움 <strong>퓨마</strong>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="ht-hot-act ht-section-items">
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
<section>
    <div class="ht-section-tt">
        요즘 많이 찾는 인기 여행지 Best
    </div>
    <div class="ht-section-cont">
        <ul class="ht-best-act ht-section-items">
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="ht-sect-tra">
    <div class="ht-section-tt">
        감성을 자극하는 여행자들의 이야기
    </div>
    <div class="ht-section-cont">
        <div class="ht-view-all">
            View All
        </div>
        <ul class="ht-travel ht-section-items">
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/tra-act1.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    <div class="ht-tra-head">
                        THERE's Travel
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-tit">
                        부엉이를 즐기센!
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-subtit">
                        맹금류의 아름다움
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-editor">
                        Edited by HANBIT<br>
                    from THERE
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/tra-act2.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    <div class="ht-tra-head">
                        THERE's Travel
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-tit">
                        창공을 날아보세!
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-subtit">
                        맹금류의 멋짐
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-editor">
                        Edited by HANBIT<br>
                        from THERE
                    </div>
            </li>
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/tra-act3.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    <div class="ht-tra-head">
                        THERE's Travel
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-tit">
                        슈르륵 멋짐의 폭발!
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-subtit">
                        아름다운 선의 미학
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-tra-editor">
                        Edited by HANBIT<br>
                        from THERE
                    </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="ht-sect-review">
    <div class="ht-section-tt">
        놓치면 후회 할 리얼 후기 Review
    </div>
    <div class="ht-section-cont">
        <div class="ht-view-all">
            View All
        </div>
        <ul class="ht-review ht-section-items">
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/rv-act1.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    <div class="ht-review-tt">
                        Travel's Review
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-review-sub-tt">
                        리뷰를 찾아 여기저기 돌아다니는 것은 그만!<br>
                        이제 THERE, 한곳에서 확인하세요
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    <div class="ht-rv-img" style="background-image: url(./img/rv-act2.jpg)">
                        <div class="dark-layer"></div>
                        </div>
                    <div class="ht-rv-tt">
                        싱가폴 자유여행은 센토사 섬에서!
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-rv-sub-tt">
                        싱가폴에서 하루는 센토사 섬<br>
                        유니버셜 스튜디오에서
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-rv-edit">
                        by 투투투(jake7297)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    <div class="ht-rv-img" style="background-image: url(./img/rv-act3.jpg)">
                        <div class="dark-layer"></div>
                        </div>
                    <div class="ht-rv-tt">
                        싱가폴 자유여행은 센토사 섬에서!
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-rv-sub-tt">
                        싱가폴에서 하루는 센토사 섬<br>
                        유니버셜 스튜디오에서
                    </div>
                    <div class="ht-rv-edit">
                        by 투투투(jake7297)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
{{> template/footer}}

</body>
</html>